  "remarks": "JSC “Sarapulsky Radiozavod” creates innovative radio communication technologies, mainly for mobile systems and devices across various platforms. Its products are used in the armoured personnel carrier Tiger-M and in systems such as “Arbalet” and “Akveduk”, all of which are used by Russia in its war of aggression against Ukraine.",
